					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The whole picture (at least by Rec. 601 definition of active picture period) is 280x240, including 24 pixels of side border (12 on each side). Multiply 280/240 by 8/7 (pixel aspect ratio) to get 4/3 (display aspect ratio).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

